sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User (RAD UI)
    participant API as RAD Backend API
    participant FS as Firestore
    participant PS as Pub/Sub
    participant CF as Cloud Function
    participant CB as Cloud Build
    participant TF as Terraform
    participant GCP as GCP Resources

    User->>API: Submit Deployment Request
    API->>FS: Create Deployment Document (QUEUED)
    FS-->>API: Document Created
    API->>PS: Publish Deployment Message
    PS-->>API: Message Published
    API-->>User: Deployment Queued
    
    PS->>CF: Trigger Cloud Function
    CF->>CB: Start Cloud Build Pipeline
    CB->>FS: Update Status (PROVISIONING)
    FS-->>User: Real-time Status Update
    
    CB->>CB: Clone Git Repository
    CB->>TF: terraform init
    CB->>TF: terraform apply
    TF->>GCP: Create Resources
    GCP-->>TF: Resources Created
    TF-->>CB: Deployment Complete
    
    CB->>FS: Update Status (SUCCESS)
    FS-->>User: Real-time Status Update
    User->>FS: View Deployment Logs
    FS-->>User: Display Logs
